            <title>[LU-18202] fix LB_USES_DPKG to check distro</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18202</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some cluster manager by default installs dpkg on its centos/rhel installation - presumably to allow provisioning debian nodes in the cluster, so dpkg is in the path and can&apos;t be removed.&lt;br/&gt;
